
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Consulting";
}
<h2>Frequent Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
<div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
                What courses are offered by the college?
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">The college offers a wide range of undergraduate and postgraduate programs designed to meet the educational needs of students from different academic backgrounds. 
                Some of the popular courses include BCA, BBA, B.Com, BA, and B.Sc. These programs focus on both theoretical knowledge and practical skills to help students build a strong foundation for their 
                future careers.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
                How can students apply for admission?
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
            <div class="accordion-body"> Students can apply for admission through the official college website by filling out the online application form. They need to provide basic personal details, 
                educational qualifications, and upload the required documents. Alternatively, students can also visit the college admission office and complete the admission process offline with 
                the help of the admission staff.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                What are the eligibility criteria for admission?
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">The eligibility criteria depend on the course selected by the student. Generally, applicants must have successfully completed their 12th grade from a 
                recognized board. Some courses may require specific subjects or a minimum percentage of marks. Students are advised to check the admission guidelines for detailed eligibility requirements.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

<div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseFour">
                Does the college provide placement opportunities?
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes, the college has a dedicated placement cell that works to provide students with internship and job opportunities. The placement cell organizes training 
                sessions, career guidance programs, and campus recruitment drives where various companies visit the college to hire students. This helps students start their professional careers 
                after completing their studies.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>


